        "main": true,
        "title": "ProDentim® | Official Website | Healthy Gum & Teeth",
        "meta_descr": "ProDentim is a cutting-edge oral health supplement designed to restore and maintain a balanced oral microbiome. Packed with 3.5 billion probiotic strains and beneficial bacteria, it actively supports your teeth health.",
        "header_custom": "",
