          "_name": "content8",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content8\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Mark\" name=\"mark\" checked condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <select title=\"Type\" name=\"countersType\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n            <option value=\"default\" selected>Ð¡ircle Fill</option>\n            <option value=\"circle\">Circle</option>\n            <option value=\"square\">Square</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#56a21a\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Shape your future web project with the Mobirise app.\n                </h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article><p>ProDentim is your partner in keeping your mouth healthy! This innovative oral health supplement </p><p>is packed with 3.5 billion beneficial bacteria and essential nutrients to support strong teeth and </p><p>healthy gums.</p><p>\n</p><div>\n</div><div>ProDentim focuses on restoring the natural balance of good bacteria in your mouth. This </div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\">dissolvable candy slowly releases probiotics, creating a nurturing environment for these friendly microbes to thrive and maintain your oral health.</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>Its doctor-designed formula combines five powerful and clinically proven probiotic strains, adding up to 3.5 billion good bacteria in every dose. This makes ProDentim an effective and unique way to care for your teeth and gums.</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>ProDentim isn't designed to replace your regular toothpaste but rather to complement it. By delivering a special probiotic mix, it boosts the growth of beneficial bacteria in your mouth, giving you an added layer of oral protection.</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>But ProDentim doesn't stop at your mouth! By promoting a balanced oral microbiome, it also supports your respiratory health, reducing the likelihood of allergies and providing benefits beyond conventional oral care products.</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>ProDentim offers additional health perks. Its probiotics contribute to better sleep and smoother digestion, making it a comprehensive solution for improving your overall well-being.</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>Take one ProDentim candy daily. Consistent use ensures that these beneficial probiotics work continuously to keep your mouth and body in great health.</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>In short, ProDentim offers a fresh approach to oral health. It helps restore the balance of good bacteria while delivering added benefits to your overall health, making it far more impactful than regular dental products.\n</div><div><br></div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div><p></p></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
