              "ul": {
                "margin": "0",
                "list-style": "none",
                "padding-left": "2.5rem",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem",
                  "position": "relative",
                  "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "content": "\"\"",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background-color": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "& when (@countersType = \"circle\")": {
                        "background": "none",
                        "border": "1px solid @iconColor",
                        "color": "@iconColor"
                      },
                      "& when (@countersType = \"square\")": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      },
                      "& when (@mark)": {
                        "content": "\"âœ“\""
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "& when not (@stylizedCounters)": {
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-1.6rem",
                      "content": "\"\\2022\"",
                      "color": "@iconColor",
                      "font-weight": "bold",
                      "font-size": "2rem",
                      "width": "1.6rem",
                      "line-height": "1.2"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text UL": {
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content8",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content8\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized\" name=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Mark\" name=\"mark\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <select title=\"Type\" name=\"countersType\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n            <option value=\"default\" selected>Ð¡ircle Fill</option>\n            <option value=\"circle\">Circle</option>\n            <option value=\"square\">Square</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#037953\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Shape your future web project with the Mobirise app.\n                </h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><b>Lactobacillus Paracasei:&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\">This probiotic strain is known for its ability to support gum health and strengthen teeth. It also helps reduce inflammation and creates a healthy balance in the oral microbiome, which is vital for maintaining overall oral hygiene.</span></li><li><b>Lactobacillus Reuteri:</b><b style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\">&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\">Another essential probiotic, it works to reduce gum sensitivity and combat inflammation in the mouth. By promoting the growth of good bacteria, it restores the balance necessary for a healthy oral environment.</span></li></ul><ul><li><b>Bifidobacterium Lactis BL-04:</b>&nbsp;This strain supports not only oral health but also immune system function. It prevents the growth of harmful bacteria that cause bad breath and other dental issues, keeping the oral microbiome balanced.</li></ul><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Inulin:</b>&nbsp;Inulin acts as a prebiotic, providing nourishment for probiotics to thrive. It enhances the growth of beneficial bacteria, improves digestion, and helps maintain a healthy balance in the oral and gut microbiome.</span></li></ul><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Malic Acid: </b>Sourced from strawberries, malic acid is a natural compound that helps maintain tooth whiteness and overall oral health. It is also known to support healthy skin and enhance overall well-being.</span></li></ul><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Peppermint:</b>&nbsp;Peppermint adds a refreshing taste to ProDentim while offering anti-inflammatory properties. It helps soothe gums, freshen breath, and prevent bacterial growth, ensuring a healthier mouth.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem;\"><b>Tricalcium Phosphate (TCP):</b> An essential mineral, TCP plays a key role in strengthening tooth enamel and promoting overall dental health. It helps protect teeth against decay and supports long-term oral wellness.</span></li><li>Note: Each of these ingredients has been carefully chosen for its proven benefits and ability to work synergistically within the ProDentim formula. Together, they create a comprehensive solution for oral health, ensuring strong teeth, healthy gums, and improved overall well-being.</li></ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uwXjBgM7Vg",
          "_anchor": "content8-52",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
