          "_name": "features7",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features7\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Cost\" name=\"showCost\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/untitled-design-46-680x450.webp\" alt=\"60 Days Money Back Guarantee Badge\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .cost, .mbr-section-btn\"><br><br><b>Try ProDentim Risk-Free:&nbsp;</b>Use ProDentim daily as directed. Incorporate the dissolvable candy into your routine and enjoy its benefits whether it's healthier teeth and gums, better digestion, improved sleep, or respiratory support.<br><br><b>See Results or Get a Full Refund:&nbsp;</b>If you are not completely satisfied with the results within 60 days, simply reach out to their customer support team to request a refund.<br><br><b>No Questions Asked:&nbsp;</b>You'll receive a 100% refund of your purchase price no questions, no hassles, and no hidden terms.<br><br>This 60-day money-back policy ensures you can explore the transformative benefits of ProDentim with zero financial risk. Your satisfaction is the top priority, making ProDentim an easy and worry-free choice for investing in your oral health and overall well-being.<br></p>\n                        <div class=\"cost\" mbr-if=\"showCost\">\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" class=\"currentcost mbr-fonts-style pr-2\" data-app-selector=\".currentcost\">$69</span>\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" class=\"oldcost mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".oldcost\">$99</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn pt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://9fe542fduya2an5n6kobrfseeg.hop.clickbank.net/?&extclid=abhi135\" class=\"btn btn-warning\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-cart-full mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>GET YOUR BOTTLE TODAY</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
