          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Terms and Conditions</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Welcome to The ProstaStream!</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">These Terms and Conditions (\"Terms\") govern your use of us-prodientim.com (the \"Website\"). By accessing or using the Website, you agree to comply with these Terms. If you do not agree with these Terms, please do not use the Website.<br><br>1. General Use<br>You agree to use the Website in accordance with all applicable local, state, national, and international laws. You must be at least 18 years of age to use the Website and its services. By using this site, you confirm that you are of legal age to form a binding contract.<br><br>2. Intellectual Property<br>All content on us-prodientim.com, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of us-prodientim.com or its content suppliers and is protected by international copyright laws. You may not copy, reproduce, or distribute any content from the Website without prior written consent.<br><br>3. Products and Services<br>The products and services offered on the Website are for informational purposes only. us-prodientim.com does not make any representations or warranties regarding the effectiveness of any products or services. The statements on the Website have not been evaluated by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) and products are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Always consult with a healthcare professional before using any product, especially if you are pregnant, nursing, taking medication, or have a medical condition.<br><br>4. Affiliate Links and Third-Party Advertisements<br>us-prodientim.com may contain links to third-party websites or advertisements for third-party products and services. These links are provided for your convenience. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites or products. Please review the policies of these third-party sites before engaging with them.<br><br>5. User Conduct<br>You agree not to use the Website for any unlawful or prohibited purpose. You must not engage in any activity that interferes with or disrupts the Websiteâ€™s functionality or other users' enjoyment of the Website. Prohibited activities include, but are not limited to, data mining, spamming, hacking, or transmitting harmful or disruptive code.<br><br>6. Privacy and Data Collection<br>Please refer to our Privacy Policy for detailed information on how we collect, use, and protect your personal data. By using the Website, you consent to the collection and use of your data as described in the Privacy Policy.<br><br>7. Disclaimer of Warranties and Limitation of Liability<br>The Website and all content, materials, and products provided are offered \"as is\" and without any warranties, express or implied. We do not warrant that the Website will be uninterrupted or error-free, nor do we make any warranties regarding the accuracy or completeness of the content.<br><br>us-prodientim.com, its affiliates, and its employees shall not be held liable for any damages, including but not limited to, direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages, arising from the use or inability to use the Website or products purchased from the Website.<br><br>8. Modification of Terms<br>We reserve the right to modify or update these Terms at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. By continuing to use the Website after such changes, you agree to be bound by the updated Terms.<br><br>9. Indemnification<br>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless FitnessDonkey.com, its affiliates, officers, employees, and agents from any claims, losses, liabilities, and expenses arising from your use of the Website, violation of these Terms, or infringement of any intellectual property rights.<br><br>10. Termination<br>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to the Website if you violate these Terms or engage in any activities that may harm the Website or other users. Upon termination, all provisions of these Terms that by their nature should survive termination will remain in effect.<br><br>11. Governing Law<br>These Terms will be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of [Insert State], without regard to its conflict of law principles. Any dispute related to these Terms shall be resolved in the courts located in [Insert Jurisdiction].<br><br>12. Contact Us<br>If you have any questions or concerns about these Terms, please contact us at: contact@us-prodientim.com<br><br>By using the Website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
